  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cerebellar vermis anomalies are present in schizophrenic individuals. This condition leads to
      postural balance problems. Foot and ankle complex have a special role for maintaining
      balance. However, there is no study about this topic in schizophrenic individuals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
